Sometimes, we want to share as easy as possible our files, without a big and complex filemanager. This file viewer has this approach and is very easy to modify.

This project:

    Uses some Tango icons
    is based on a tutorial to generate correct headers
    Uses a hack to display correct png pictures in IE 

Last modifications

    (02.08.2008):
        Some Bugs resolved 
    (21.04.2008):
        Some Bugs resolved
        Sortable columns (Name, Size and Date modified) 